---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PicoVoice vs Booth"
  description="PicoVoiceとBoothの違いを比較"
  path="/picovoice-vs-booth"
  type="article"
>
  <section class="card">
    <small class="meta">Comparison</small>
    <h1>PicoVoice vs Booth</h1>
    <p>用途が重なる部分はありますが、設計思想は異なります。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>比較表</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>項目</th>
          <th>PicoVoice</th>
          <th>Booth</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>主な対象</td>
          <td>短尺ボイス販売</td>
          <td>幅広いデジタル商品</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>商品の長さ</td>
          <td>約30秒の短尺中心</td>
          <td>形式の制約が少ない</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>販売期間モデル</td>
          <td>期間限定販売を前提に設計</td>
          <td>常設販売が中心</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>購入体験</td>
          <td>ストリーミング / ダウンロード を用途別に選択</td>
          <td>一般的なデジタルダウンロード購入</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>ポジショニング</td>
          <td>VTuber voice marketplace に特化</td>
          <td>総合型クリエイターマーケット</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>In English</h2>
    <p>PicoVoice focuses on short, limited-time voice clips with Streaming / Download options, while Booth is a broader marketplace for many digital product types. PicoVoice is positioned as a VTuber voice marketplace.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
